# Per-model run dirs are generated by run.sh (each a throwaway git repo with its
# own state, logs, and MODEL-AUTHORED bundle). They are reproducible, never
# committed, and kept out of the repo linter's path -- `machine create` lints
# them with `ruff --isolated`, not this repo's ruleset. Only run.sh, README.md,
# and results.jsonl are tracked.
*/
!.gitignore
